</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>GPIO Pins  &lt;--->   Relay Pins
</span><span class='line'>    5V      &lt;-->        VCC
</span><span class='line'>    GND     &lt;-->        GND
</span><span class='line'>    PIN 17  &lt;-->        IND1&lt;/p>
